# epicsdev
Helper module for creating EPICS PVAccess servers.

Demo:
```
python pip install epicsdev
python -m epicsdev.epicsdev -l
```

To control and plot:
```
python pip install pypeto,pvplot
python -m pypeto -c config -f epicsdev
```


